{
  "texts": [
    "As shown in Table A2, our fast DPO model implementation achieves a 27.48% speed improvement.",
    "All the training experiments in this paper were conducted on 4×A100 80GB GPUs.",
    "We used Deepspeed (Rasley et al., 2020) for all our experiments as we find that storingin model weights in fp32 is essential for DPO's performance as learning rate is small.",
    "For other training details, please see Table A3 and Table A4.",
    "Following our findings in Section 3, we train the LION series using a combination of datasets from the instruction-tuning domain and the preference learning domain."
  ]
}